This is for an arduino uno.
The DHT's red wire is connected to pin 7
The gold wire is connected to pin 8
the black wire goes to GND
The BPM's VCC goes to pin 6
The BPM's GND to ground
The BPM's SCL to A5
The BPM's SDA to A4
The two others are not used
The SD logger's MOSI to pin 11
The SD logger's MISO to pin 12
The SD logger's CLK to pin 13
The SD logger's CS to pin 4
The SD logger's 3.3v to 3.3v
The SD logger's GND to ground 
DO NOT USE THE PIN 10 FOR ANY PURPOSES!
